00:00:00,300 --> 00:00:03,210
A lot of current efforts in healthcare
are about processing the massive

2
00:00:03,210 --> 00:00:05,850
quantities of data that
are recorded everyday.

3
00:00:05,850 --> 00:00:07,230
But in order to make that data useful,

4
00:00:07,230 --> 00:00:09,680
it has to connect to real
people at some point.

5
00:00:09,680 --> 00:00:13,370
Maybe it's equipping doctors with tools
to more easily visually evaluate and

6
00:00:13,370 --> 00:00:15,400
compare different diagnoses.

7
00:00:15,400 --> 00:00:18,220
Maybe it's giving patients the tools
necessary to monitor their own health

8
00:00:18,220 --> 00:00:19,780
and treatment options.

9
00:00:19,780 --> 00:00:21,550
Maybe that's information
visualization so

10
