decisions affect their well-being.

11
00:00:24,850 --> 00:00:27,720
Maybe it's context aware computing that
can detect when patients are about to do

12
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:29,000
something they probably shouldn't do.

13
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:33,550
There are also numerous applications of
HCI to personal health like Fitbit for

14
