MyFitnessPal for tracking your diet.

15
00:00:36,830 --> 00:00:40,110
Those interfaces succeed if
they're easily usable for users.

16
00:00:40,110 --> 00:00:42,220
Ideally, they'd be almost invisible.

17
00:00:42,220 --> 00:00:44,850
But perhaps the most fascinating
upcoming intersection of HCI and

18
