what about virtual reality for therapy?

21
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,730
That's actually already happening.

22
00:00:55,730 --> 00:00:58,130
We can use virtual reality to
help people confront fears and

23
00:00:58,130 --> 00:01:01,470
anxieties in a safe, but
highly authentic place.

24
00:01:01,470 --> 00:01:04,450
Healthcare in general is concerned
with the health of humans.

25
00:01:04,450 --> 00:01:07,110
And computers are pretty commonly
used in modern healthcare.

26
00:01:07,110 --> 00:01:09,660
